                <h1>What is the Met Gala? Unravel the Glamour!</h1>
                <p>The Met Gala, officially called the Costume Institute Gala, is an annual fundraising event for the Metropolitan Museum of Art’s Costume Institute in New York City. Celebrities and influencers showcase extravagant outfits that reflect the evening’s theme. It marks the opening of the year’s fashion exhibition, blending high fashion with art.</p>
